data.description: Newly remodeled home in an established neighborhood in Fort Smith. Beautiful eat-in kitchen with granite counters, tile backsplash, new kitchen cabinets, new roof and laundry hookups.  The main bedroom has a jacuzzi bathtub and the home has one full bath.  Fresh paint throughout, inside and out.  The front porch swing is the perfect place to sit and enjoy the weather.  A small storage shed is on-site.  This adorable home won't last long.  Call and schedule a showing!
